data.text:
Driven by a Common Purpose

Although Korsmo Construction is made up of many unique individuals, we all have one thing in common: we care. From carpenters to project managers, accountants to estimators, and project engineers to superintendents, members of the Korsmo team are truly passionate about their trade. We are driven, hard-working people who truly enjoy serving our clients to build lasting relationships. No matter the conditions, our crews will provide a quality finished project you can depend on.
